# GrayOcean

Vite + React 18 SaaS (JSX, not TSX). Alias `@/*` → `src/*`.

## Layout

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `src/pages/*.jsx` | Auth workspace (SSN, Address, Batch, Skiptrace…) |
| `src/pages/site/**` | Marketing + auth marketing |
| `src/components/ui/**` | shadcn — reuse, don't fork |
| `src/components/{ssn,address,batch,marketing}/**` | Feature UI |
| `src/api/localClient.js` | localStorage Base44 stand-in |
| `src/entities/*.js` | Thin wrappers over `db.entities.*` |
| `base44/entities/*.jsonc` | Schema docs |
| `src/index.css` | `--go-*` tokens |
| `src/pages.config.js` | Workspace registry (edit imports + `PAGES`) |
| `src/Layout.jsx` | Workspace chrome / sidebar |
| `src/App.jsx` | Marketing routes |

## Defaults

- Imports: `@/…`
- Icons: `lucide-react`
- Lists: `@tanstack/react-query`
- Style: Tailwind + `var(--go-*)` only
- Auth: local auto-dev user — don't rebuild Base44 SDK unless asked
